Rest assured that when you book with me the car will be available and ready for your use when you arrive.  As an experienced host with over 1000 trips I am aware of your concerns and I will do my very best to make this as smooth as possible.  I am a Turo All-star host and a top rated Power host.  I am attentive and responsive.  If you have any questions, before, during or after your trip just let me know and I will get back to you promptly.

I always use Turo Go or remote handoff for contact free delivery. I will share a link with you and you will be able to use your phone to unlock the car. Before you arrive I will send you detailed instructions for how to access the car and the keys.

If you are flying into Tampa, you can save on airport tax by having the car delivered to Homewood Suites on Avion Drive.  They will provide a free shuttle from the airport.  If you want the car a little faster then go ahead and book for TPA delivery.  The car will be ready and waiting in the Airport Economy Parking lot.

If you do not wish to pay for delivery my home lot is located in Downtown St. Petersburg, about a 25 minute car ride from the airport.  Lyft/Uber fees can range from about $30-$75 depending on driver availability and demand.

I also deliver to PIE and select beach locations.

When you rent a car from me it will be cleaned and sanitized on the interior and, weather permitting, clean on the exterior.  I do not expect you to clean the car before you return it unless there is a significant mess inside.  I just ask that you do not leave me your trash.

I offer a prepaid refuel option so that you can save time upon return and not have to worry about finding a gas station.

All of my cars are equipped with Sunpass toll transponders.  Guests are responsible for all tolls incurred during the trip.  You will save time and money using Sunpass.
